Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽說服裝已經到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}道具放哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下面開始彩排
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幸好趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然考究一些是沒有錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼我接下來還要去準備其他同學的服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.42,0:01:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會長在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她正投入編排舞台劇 好像抽不開身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明白了 是公主出演的劇目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼各位 把這次當做正式演出再來一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}音樂 請從最開始演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是小露的服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我用了超級顯眼的設計
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行 還是好緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}美如畫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼 只是覺得衣服和你很配
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有怪怪的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一點也不會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我還是覺得這個角色更適合安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 是大家都說想看古蕾婭的公主裝扮的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自信些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是我沒穿過這種輕飄飄的衣服 總是有些緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會有問題的 畢竟練習了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺肚子好像開始痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:02:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}具體哪裡痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我馬上幫你治好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒…沒事的 我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不是很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}覺得難受時記得立即告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼那邊交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你去負責那邊的修正
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很快就能準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\an8}不要忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼從開場部分開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}照明要確保和音響同步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們再對一遍台詞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昨天睡前還有今天過來前 我都有好好練習
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能演好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吸—吸—呼— 吸—吸—呼—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吸氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呼氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事的 有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}浮一下試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}浮？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想像 想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手腳要放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放鬆下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}睜開眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請務必注視著我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有什麼好害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}台詞？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在恐懼的內心中迴響的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}並不是來自反對你的大地之民的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而是你自己缺乏自信的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絕望累積成疾 折磨著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而我不禁躊躇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是否邁出這一步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…需要你！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}王子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有什麼好害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就是那黎明的鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}將我拯救的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜託兩位了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:07:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}公主 沒有什麼好害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要你我在一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}願陪您一同前往 王子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}滿座
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}加油 漢娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太棒了 漢娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下來輪到我們了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感覺肚子好像開始痛了
